checkers.fenum.quals

Annotation Type AwtColorSpace


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={TYPE_USE,TYPE_PARAMETER})
 @TypeQualifier
 @SubtypeOf(value=FenumTop.class)
public @interface AwtColorSpace
    Color space tags to identify the specific color space of a Color object or, via a ColorModel object, of an Image, a BufferedImage, or a GraphicsDevice (see ColorSpace for more details).
    See Also:
    ColorSpace.TYPE_XYZ, ColorSpace.TYPE_Lab, ColorSpace.TYPE_Luv, ColorSpace.TYPE_YCbCr, ColorSpace.TYPE_Yxy, ColorSpace.TYPE_RGB, ColorSpace.TYPE_GRAY, ColorSpace.TYPE_HSV, ColorSpace.TYPE_HLS, ColorSpace.TYPE_CMYK, ColorSpace.TYPE_CMY, ColorSpace.TYPE_2CLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_3CLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_4CLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_5CLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_6CLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_7CLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_8CLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_9CLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_ACLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_BCLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_CCLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_DCLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_ECLR, ColorSpace.TYPE_FCLR, ColorSpace.CS_sRGB, ColorSpace.CS_LINEAR_RGB, ColorSpace.CS_CIEXYZ, ColorSpace.CS_PYCC, ColorSpace.CS_GRAY
